      <div class="section">
        <h2>3. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All intellectual property rights related to Blanq — including design, algorithms, logo, and content — are owned by its developers or licensors. You may not copy, distribute, or modify any part of the app without prior authorization.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>Blanq is provided “as is” without any warranty of specific medical or dental outcomes. The app’s recommendations are for informational purposes only and should not replace professional dental advice.</p>
        <div class="highlight-box">
          <p><strong>Note:</strong> If you experience dental issues, please consult a qualified dentist before following any recommendations from the app.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>5. Changes to the Terms</h2>
        <p>We may update these Terms of Service at any time. Users will be notified via the app or email. Continued use of Blanq after any modification constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.</p>
